snippet: What has compelled Ukrainians to take to the streets and protest?
abstract: What has compelled Ukrainians to take to the streets and protest?
lead_paragraph: In the article “Kiev Teems With Pro-Europe Protesters as Thousands More Gather” David M. Herszenhorn and Andrew E. Kramer write about the rally and what its participants want to see change in their country.

headline.main: 6 Q’s About the News | Hundreds of Thousands Protest in Kiev
